data.description: Bring the offers! Great location. Close to Chesterfield Village, The Medical Mile. Preferred Kickapoo School District. New Covenant Accademy. Universities and the best shopping. Easy access to main routes. One street outside city limits in Greene Co. Very quiet area. 95% remodeled, unique, rustic, with a touch of modernHigh efficiency gas water tank 2019 New Heat and 96.5% A/C system 2021 New Roof 2021 both have transferable warranty 2021 Custom Red Cedar compliments the Arkansas field stone. New vynl siding, shutters, gutters, down spouts, soffit and facia All insulation was removed and replaced with ecco fiber blow in Attic with insulation under the floor when attic was added, giving 800SF of storage Patio's front and back with connecting sidewalk all have decorative stamping   There is a hand laid stone fire-pit in the back yard, with 3 mature trees and a cedar garden in the front of the house. All but two rooms have been remodeled. One bathroom and laundry. There is lots of custom woodwork throughout the house. All the wood used in this home is from Missouri timber grown, sawn & milled. The trim detail is red oak. There are 9 custom made barn doors in all. #2 Cabin grade hardwood floors & tile are allergy friendly. Main bathroom remodeled in tile and granite. The floor plan was changed to make the  nook larger & flow to a dining area adding to the houses open floor plan. The great room has a hand laid stone fireplace w/ red cedar beam/ tile landing. All the rooms have new ceiling light/ fans. Some have Alexa compatible switch's Bedroom and hallway closets are lined w/ aromatic red cedar. New solid oak doors to rooms. New front door allows more natural light yet offer privacy. New custom made french doors have built in blinds. There is a nice view through open doors and retractable screens, that flows out to the back patio, to the fireplace. The ceilings are  hand troweled texture. The kitchen has granite countertops & black glazed cast iron jacuzzi sink
